nhc_headline: ...JERRY MOVING NORTHWARD OVER THE WESTERN ATLANTIC...
summary: ...JERRY MOVING NORTHWARD OVER THE WESTERN ATLANTIC... As of 5:00 AM AST Sat Oct 11 the center of Jerry was located near 24.5, -63.4 with movement N at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
